      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. i guess i'm just nervous about the \"irreparable harm\" part and the \"injunctive relief\" bit. it sounds pretty intense. could you explain what that actually means in plain English? like, what's the worst case scenario if i accidentally leak something?",
